result.name: Sanger Institute Mouse Genomes Project v5
result.description: SNP and INDEL calls from version 5 of the Mouse Genome Project at the Wellcome Trust Sanger Institute. Specifically, this project describes the variants of 36 mouse strains aligned against the reference mouse genome sequence GRCm38.
result.platform: Illumina HiSeq 2000, Illumina Genome Analyzer II
